      <title>亚马逊的付款延迟警告引起 Flex 司机的恐慌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/amazon-s-payment-delay-warning-stirs-panic-among-flex-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社审阅的信件显示，亚马逊公司警告使用自有车辆运送包裹的 Flex 司机，他们原定于周四收到的付款“可能会延迟”，这引起了习惯于在完成路线后立即付款的司机的恐慌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/amazon-s-payment-delay-warning-stirs-panic-among-flex-drivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:40:13 GMT</pubDate>
